							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="QTypealone"><strong>QUESTIONS TO MEMBERS</strong></p><h4 class="QSubjectHeading"><strong>Questions</strong><strong> No. 1 and 2 to Member</strong></h4><p class="Speech"><a name="time_20161102 15:14:00" ></a><strong>Mr SPEAKER</strong>: We would normally move now to questions to members, but I am aware that the chair of the Local Government and Environment Committee is not present in the House. Those two questions are therefore held over until tomorrow.</p><p class="QOAEnd"><a name="time_20161102 15:14:17 " ></a><strong> </strong></p></div></body>
